# Supabase Security

- `src/lib/supabase/admin.ts` is server-only — never import in Client Components or `"use client"` modules.
- `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` only in server env (Route Handlers, Server Actions, Server Components).
- Browser code uses `client.ts` with anon key only; SSR uses `server.ts` with cookies.
- Enable RLS on exposed tables; never authorize via `user_metadata` in policies.

